>[Question]
>What is the key to multiplying, subtracting, adding, dividing and 
>divideing fractons of intergers? And what if there are three or four
>numbers to multiply or addition or subraction?
>
>[Difficulty]
>There is more than just 2 numbers, and it's hard to figure out if 
>your dividing or dividing fractions.
